      "firm_id": "sybil_2",
      "description": "This E46 M3 features the legendary S54 naturally aspirated inline-six, delivering linear power to the rear wheels via a crisp Getrag 6-speed manual transmission. The chassis remains taut with upgraded bushings and documented subframe reinforcement, addressing the primary structural concerns of this platform. Recent service includes a comprehensive VANOS overhaul and rod bearing replacement, ensuring the high-revving internals are optimized for performance. Equipped with a functional limited-slip differential and staggered alloys, this driver\u2019s example offers visceral engagement and precise turn-in response for the discerning purist.",
